Hints: #177, #182, #263, #342

10.2	How do you check if two words are anagrams of each other? Think about what the defiÂ¬nition of "anagram" is. Explain it in your own words.

10.2	Two words are anagrams if they contain the same characters but in different orders. How can you put characters in order?

10.2	Can you leverage a standard sorting algorithm?

10.2	Do you even need to truly "sort"? Or is just reorganizing the list sufficient?
